    <title><![CDATA[github pages 下 hexo 搭建静态博客试水]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.elegantwww.com/2015/09/10/blog1/"/>
    <id>http://www.elegantwww.com/2015/09/10/blog1/</id>
    <published>2015-09-10T04:56:31.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-09-12T11:39:42.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="引用">引用</h2><p><a href="http://cnfeat.com/blog/2014/05/10/how-to-build-a-blog/" target="_blank" rel="external">cnFeat</a><br><a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/zhcncn/" target="_blank" rel="external">金石开</a><br><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/setup.html" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo官网</a><br><a href="http://litten.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo下主题yilia</a></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="总结">总结</h2><p>[toc]</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="选择">选择</h2><ol>
<li>github pages + hexo</li>
<li><strong>支持markdown是必须的</strong>：typecho也是可以的</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="github_步骤">github 步骤</h2><ol>
<li><p><strong>配置SSH keys</strong>: Git shell, </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><strong>生成新的SSH Key</strong>:  后回车</p>
<figure class="highlight mathematica"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -<span class="keyword">C</span> <span class="string">"邮件地址@youremail.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>打开C:\Users\Zing4.ssh下的id_rsa.pub</p>
</li>
<li>在web上的用户setting下的ssh keys下add:</li>
<li><p>测试</p>
<figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">ssh</span> -T git<span class="variable">@github</span>.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>设置用户信息</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user<span class="class">.name</span> <span class="string">"elegantwww"</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user<span class="class">.email</span> <span class="string">"elegantwww@gmail.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<a id="more"></a>
<hr>
<h2 id="hexo_步骤">hexo 步骤</h2><ol>
<li>安装 node.js</li>
<li>node-v4.0.0-x64.msi  </li>
<li><strong>a dll required for this install to complete could not be run.</strong>【<strong>解决</strong>用v0.10.40/x64/替代】 <img src="http://127.0.0.1:8912/api/file/getImage?fileId=55f05c194f71f32089000000" alt=""></li>
<li>配置pages: 仓库名必须为【your_user_name.github.io】</li>
<li><strong>安装hexo</strong>:  <figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="调试">调试</h2><ol>
<li>新建hexo文件夹  C:\Users\Zing4\Documents\GitHub\hexo</li>
<li><p><strong>初始化</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd hexo</span><br><span class="line">hexo init <span class="preprocessor">#初始化</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">server</span> <span class="preprocessor">#启动服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><strong>部署</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> “这里是博客名字”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>改 _config.yml</p>
<figure class="highlight haskell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="preprocessor"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="preprocessor">##  Docs: http://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title">deploy</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="typedef"><span class="keyword">type</span>: git</span></span><br><span class="line">  repository: git@github.com:elegantwww/elegantwww.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch:master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>【错误 type: github】</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="operator"><span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-deployer-git <span class="comment">--save</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<p>修改配置文件<br>将_config.yml中<br>deploy 的 type由github改为git。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="新建文章">新建文章</h2><ol>
<li><p><strong>新建文章</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="string">"文章题目"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><strong>页面</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> page <span class="string">"1"</span> <span class="preprocessor">#面面链接名称</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><strong>生成静态文件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">hexo</span> generate  <span class="comment"># 简写：hexo g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><strong>服务器</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">server</span> <span class="preprocessor"># 简写：hexo s</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><strong>部署到git</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">hexo</span> deploy <span class="comment"># 简写：hexo d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<p>##部署后网页有显示有问题<br><figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">g</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="literal">d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="删除文章">删除文章</h2><p>**直接删除.md</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="图床">图床</h2><p><strong>七牛</strong></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="yilia_改字体">yilia 改字体</h2><p>打开 GitHub\hexo\themes\yilia\source\css\style.styl<br><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">body</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="rule"><span class="attribute">font-family</span>:<span class="value"> <span class="string">"微软雅黑"</span>,<span class="string">"HelveticaNeue-Light"</span>,<span class="string">"Helvetica Neue Light"</span>,<span class="string">"Helvetica Neue"</span>,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="rule"><span class="attribute">font-size</span>:<span class="value"><span class="number">16px</span></span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="rule"><span class="attribute">background</span>:<span class="value"><span class="hexcolor">#fff</span></span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="rule"><span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="value"> <span class="function">rgba</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0.8</span>)</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p> color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);:最后一个是透明度。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="评论">评论</h2><p>修改GitHub\hexo\themes\yilia_config.yml内的，<br><figure class="highlight http"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">duoshuo</span>: <span class="string">elegantwww</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="文章">文章</h2><ol>
<li>题目可以直接在_post下的md文件改下就行了。</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="购买域名-失败">购买域名-失败</h2><ol>
<li><a href="www.godaddy.com">godaddy</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.dute.me/" target="_blank" rel="external">优惠码</a> </li>
<li><a href="http://www.laodong.me/" target="_blank" rel="external">老董优惠码</a><br>选择的是，35%，CJCRMN35</li>
<li>【问题】首先是出现：There was a problem processing your transaction. Please verify your payment information or use an alternate form of payment.</li>
<li>换了优惠码，却发现支付总是不能减免，故放弃。</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="万网购买">万网购买</h2><ol>
<li>使用 <strong>阿里云-万网服务</strong></li>
<li>购买了域名后，<strong>云解析</strong>。（查ip，并把ip 指向网站）</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<p>##将独立域名与GitHub Pages的空间绑定</p>
<ul>
<li><p>方法一：在Repository的根目录下面，新建一个名为CNAME的文本文件，里面写入你要绑定的域名，比如baidu.com。<strong>此处建议加上www.baidu.com, 不然，地址栏只不会有www.</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p>方法二：到我的github仓库，点击右下角的「Download ZIP」，下载源文件，解压，找到CNAME文件，用记事本打开，将cnfeat.com修改成你的域名，放进Hexo\source目录下，用hexo命令提交上去。</p>
<figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">d</span> -<span class="keyword">g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="DNS设置">DNS设置</h2><ol>
<li>www.dnspod.cn</li>
<li>注册-添加域名-导入主机记录</li>
<li>CNAME:  elegantwww.github.io</li>
<li>再把dns 填到域名商处（万网）</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="网站图标">网站图标</h2><ol>
<li>比特虫 制做ico ： <a href="http://www.bitbug.net/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://www.bitbug.net/</a></li>
<li><p>看一下hexo\themes\modernist\layout_partial\head.ejs，找到这句：</p>
<figure class="highlight erb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">link</span> <span class="attribute">rel</span>=<span class="value">"icon"</span> <span class="attribute">href</span>=<span class="value">"</span></span></span>&lt;%-<span class="ruby"> theme.favicon </span>%&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag"><span class="value">"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>将favicon.ico放到工程根目录下即可，也就是hexo\source目录。</p>
</li>
<li>备注代码：<figure class="highlight erb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">link</span> <span class="attribute">rel</span>=<span class="value">"icon"</span> <span class="attribute">type</span>=<span class="value">"image/x-icon"</span> <span class="attribute">href</span>=<span class="value">"</span></span></span>&lt;%-<span class="ruby"> config.root </span>%&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag"><span class="value">favicon.ico"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="摘要文字_（太有用了）">摘要文字 （<strong>太有用了</strong>）</h2><p>在摘要文字后面插入<br><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="生成_post_时默认生成_categories_配置项">生成 post 时默认生成 categories 配置项</h2><p>在 scaffolds/post.md 中添加<br><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="label">categories:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="添加_fork_me_on_github">添加 fork me on github</h2><ul>
<li>官方教程： <a href="https://github.com/blog/273-github-ribbons" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/blog/273-github-ribbons</a></li>
<li><p>将代码粘贴到 themes\ ? \layout\layout.ejs中，放置在 最后，标签之前即可：</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;<span class="tag">a</span> href=<span class="string">"https://github.com/elegantwww"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="tag">img</span> style=<span class="string">"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; border: 0;"</span> src=<span class="string">"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/8b6b8ccc6da3aa5722903da7b58eb5ab1081adee/68747470733a2f2f73332e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f6769746875622f726962626f6e732f666f726b6d655f6c6566745f6f72616e67655f6666373630302e706e67"</span> alt=<span class="string">"Fork me on GitHub"</span> data-canonical-src=<span class="string">"https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_left_orange_ff7600.png"</span>&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>由于yilia 主题左边是固定的，而把缎带放在右上角会遮住时间戳，所以把其中 position: absolute 改为 fixed.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="rss_(未成功)">rss (未成功)</h2><ol>
<li><p>安装插件</p>
<figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-generator-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>全局配置文件开启插件</p>
<figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>hexo-generator-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>主题配置文件添加入口</p>
<figure class="highlight http"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">rss</span>: <span class="string">/atom.xml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="网站地图（未成功）">网站地图（未成功）</h2><hr>
<h2 id="fancybox_（未成功）">fancybox （未成功）</h2>]]></content>
